headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 1.5X GTA$ and RP on Acid Lab Sell Missions
content:
If the Fooliganz have learned anything from recent events, it’s that people love psychedelics. Keep everyone’s third eye open with Acid Lab Sell Missions this week, paying out 50% extra GTA$ and RP.

To get started with your own Acid Lab business, head to Warstock Cache & Carry and purchase the MTL Brickade 6x6. The service vehicle comes complete with Acid Lab installation.
